 Jeff Bezos


 
Actor





Jeff Bezos was born on January 12, 1964 in Albuquerque, New Mexico, USA as Jeffrey Preston Bezos. He is an actor, known for TED: The Future We Will Create (2007), Star Trek Beyond (2016) and 60 Minutes (1968).            
See full bio »
            
 


